<div data-cid="w8DBA048E921542869158525" data-link_cid="" class="widget rich_text hleft vtop" id="widgetw8DBA048E921542869158525p" style="width: 329px; height: 70px; left: 22px; top: 90px; z-index: 536870914; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; line-height: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; opacity: 1;"><div class="rich-text"><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">你想不劳而获吗？</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">你想躺在家里赚钱吗？</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">你想月入上万且上不封顶吗？</span></p></div><div class="region gesture "></div></div>

<div data-cid="wF8BDFECFC11542869164001" data-link_cid="" class="widget rich_text hleft vtop" id="widgetwF8BDFECFC11542869164001p" style="width: 307px; height: 40px; left: 22px; top: 170px; z-index: 536870915; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; line-height: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; opacity: 1;"><div class="rich-text"><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">拒绝饮水机危害，拒绝桶装水危害，关注饮水健康！推荐亲戚朋友，免费获得赏金！</span></p></div><div class="region gesture "></div></div>
<div data-cid="w081D9E702F1542851158108" data-link_cid="" class="widget rounded_rect hcenter vmiddle" id="widgetw081D9E702F1542851158108p" style="width: 338px; height: 40px; left: 11px; top: 220px; z-index: 3; border-color: transparent; font-size: 18px; padding: 0px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; text-align: center; line-height: 26px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; opacity: 1;"><div class="text" style="padding: 0px;"><p>推荐亲戚朋友得赏金，比买彩票靠谱多了</p></div><div class="region gesture "></div></div>
<div class="rich-text"><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">1.推荐即可得到50元佣金。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">2.推荐的人每次买水能得到相应的赏金。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">如：一个朋友经过你的推荐使用上了健康智能的茶吧机，</span><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">第一次买水10袋，每袋赏金1元。</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">你能获得赏金为：</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;"> 50元（首次推荐）+1元×10（袋）= 60元</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">且以后每次买水你都能获得相应的赏金，</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">长期获得的赏金为：</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;"> 长期赏金 = 50元（首次推荐）+ n 元 × X（袋）</span></p><p style="line-height:0; margin-bottom:5px;"><span class="--mb--rich-text" data-boldtype="0" style="font-family:SourceHanSansSC; font-weight:400; font-size:14px; color:rgb(16, 16, 16); font-style:normal; letter-spacing:0px; line-height:20px; text-decoration:none;">3.最终解释权归太极兵所有。</span></p></div>




